                  <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Only if you turn on enforce-mode in week 1. The Evernow approach is: month 1 observability only, month 2 PR gating with override, month 3 hard gating for critical IaC rules. No delivery friction.{% else %}Só se ativar enforce-mode na semana 1. A abordagem Evernow é: mês 1 só observabilidade, mês 2 gating em PR com override, mês 3 hard gating em regras IaC críticas. Sem atrito com entrega.{% endif %}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card bg-transparent border-0" style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1) !important;">
              <div class="card-header bg-transparent border-0 p-0">
                <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left text-white text-decoration-none shadow-none font-weight-bold d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center py-3 px-0 collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#faqC4" aria-expanded="false">
